}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== '''Computer Essentials''' ''4 Port USB v1.1 Ultra Slim USB Hub''
This hub was sold at '''Walgreens'''.
"GM-M54HUB-2B" is silkscreened on the board. :The '''Alcor Micro''' hub IC package is marked with "ALCOR", "AU9254A21-CAS", "MGT2S-000", and "0329". :The capacitors on the board are '''Suncap''' branded.
There is no power adapter included with this device, but it does have a connector for external power
